 process is divided into segments corresponding to logical components.\"}, {\"meta\": {}, \"items\": [], \"content\": \"Segments are mapped to physical memory using segment tables.\"}], \"style\": \"ordered\"}, \"type\": \"list\"}, {\"id\": \"PSIdReb_XI\", \"data\": {\"text\": \"Advantages\", \"level\": 3}, \"type\": \"header\"}, {\"id\": \"SlhWEDlENo\", \"data\": {\"meta\": {}, \"items\": [{\"meta\": {}, \"items\": [], \"content\": \"Provides logical organization of memory.\"}, {\"meta\": {}, \"items\": [], \"content\": \"Allows easier sharing and protection of segments.\"}], \"style\": \"unordered\"}, \"type\": \"list\"}, {\"id\": \"eMV5EfNXhi\", \"data\": {\"text\": \"Challenges\", \"level\": 3}, \"type\": \"header\"}, {\"id\": \"eUCW8ylmYq\", \"data\": {\"meta\": {}, \"items\": [{\"meta\": {}, \"items\": [], \"content\": \"External fragmentation.\"}, {\"meta\": {}, \"items\": [], \"content\": \"Complex memory allocation.\"}], \"style\": \"unordered\"}, \"type\": \"list\"}, {\"id\": \"QH92M65LSs\", \"data\": {\"text\": \"Conclusion\", \"level\": 3}, \"type\": \"header\"}, {\"id\": \"zZ6f0CkitN\", \"data\": {\"text\": \"Segmentation offers a logical and flexible approach to memory management, especially for systems requiring modular memory organization.\"}, \"type\": \"paragraph\"}], \"version\": \"2.30.7\"}','2024-12-02 14:19:30.378466','Segmentation: Logical Memory Management','2024-12-02 14:19:30.378519',26,8),(74,'{\"time\": 1733123986292, \"blocks\": [{\"id\": \"nJk94jt99v\", \"data\": {\"text\": \"Introduction\", \"level\": 3}, \"type\": \"header\"}, {\"id\": \"_DzaqHQwxV\", \"data\": {\"text\": \"Memory allocation strategies determine how memory is assigned to processes, balancing efficiency and fragmentation.\"}, \"type\": \"paragraph\"}, {\"id\": \"eagmKQ-KcZ\", \"data\": {\"text\": \"Common Strategies\", \"level\": 3}, \"type\": \"header\"}, {\"id\": \"Oni_c1fjs_\", \"data\": {\"meta\": {}, \"items\": [{\"meta\": {}, \"items\": [], \"content\": \"First F